events.text:
Hey.
Listen up frog.
I've been observing your activities, the moment you fell.
Look I know you've been talking to my co-worker and he maybe more non-chalant than I am
but don't think he's just some goofball or lazy, I mean sure he's both but he is absolutely way more than you would think.
but I am obligated by law to give you a warning.
so.
I'm going to spare you this one time.
but.
If I encounter you again.
then the prince has spoken.
